- the customer sees a catalogue of 4 main products categories and beneath the catalogue a collection of pictures to the products 
- then the customer sets special requests for colors as the product consists of two parts so we should allow him to choose the colors of each part
- the allocated colors for each part should appear as color boxes
- first part preference colors:( #000000 / #36454F / #FFFFFF )
- second part preference colors: (#808080 / #F5F5DC / #F0F8FF / #4F433C / #0000FF / #40E0D0 / #30D5C8 )
- the owner wants to add facebook pixel ID : 903969498364730
- finally the customer should fill a form to complete the request containing their full name , primary phone number , second phone number, the city and a text box to insert full address and below a button to complete the purchase.
- the page should submit the customer's request and preferences to the owner's whatsapp which is: +201019550337

